snippet.title: Super Snail | AVAILABLE NOW on IOS and Android!
snippet.description:
Embark on a fantastic journey with Super Snail, an idle RPG full of memes! As a tiny snail, you must travel back a hundred years ago to save civilization from the brink of extinction. Explore Realms, collect Relics, make friends, and slay Demon Gods! Join us now for launch event rewards!

AVAILABLE NOW on IOS and Android!
https://bit.ly/Super-Snail

Discord: https://discord.gg/supersnail 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SuperSnailOf...
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/supersnailo...
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SuperSnailUS 
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@supersnailoff...
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/SuperSnail_US/ 

Subscribe to our YouTube channel for more gameplay videos!
